  <brief_title>Fosfomycin Plus Imipenem for Treatment of Infective Endocarditis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Efficacy and Safety of Fosfomycin Plus Imipenem for the Treatment of Methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus Aureus (MRSA) Infective Endocarditis.</official_title>
